  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "<span class=\"name name-fuel\">Faecium</span> is a nitrogen-rich organic material harvested from the dung of many large animals. Feed animals to increase faecium production.<br>It is possible to grow faecium given the right environment and correct host plant. Seek advice from an <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Agricultural Specialist</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "<span class=\"name name-fuel\">屎球菌</span>是一种富含氮元素的有机材料，能从许多大型动物的粪便中采集到。饲养动物来提升屎球菌的产量。<br>可以通过在适当的环境下种植恰当的寄主植物来培养出屎球菌。具体建议可咨询<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">农业专家</span>。",
    "TencentChinese": "<span class=\"name name-fuel\">屎球菌</span>是一种富含氮元素的有机材料，能从许多大型动物的粪便中采集到。饲养动物来提升屎球菌的产量。<br>可以通过在适当的环境下种植恰当的寄主植物来培养出屎球菌。具体建议可咨询<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">农业专家</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-fuel\">屎菌</span>是一種從大型動物的排泄物所採收的有機材料，氮含量高。餵食動物即可提升屎菌產量。<br>有合適的環境與宿主植物，也可種植屎菌。尋求<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">農業專家</span>的建議。"
  },
  "PinObjectiveMessage": {
    "English": "Harvest from the dung of many large animals. Feed animals to increase faecium production<br>This material can be farmed within a <span class=\"name name-commodity\">base</span> with the aid of an <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Agricultural Specialist</span>",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "采集自各类大型生物留下的粪便。喂食生物以提高屎球菌产量<br>可以在<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">农业专家</span>的帮助下于<span class=\"name name-commodity\">基地</span>中种植这种资源",
    "TraditionalChinese": "採集自多種大型動物的排泄物。餵食動物可提升屎菌產量<br>借助<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">農業專家</span>的力量即可在<span class=\"name name-commodity\">基地</span>培養這種材料"
  },
